    identified below, how we may use the information, with whom we may share it, and the choices available regarding our use of the information. The Privacy Notice also describes the measures we take to safeguard the personal information and how
    individuals can contact us about our privacy practices. Ring is the data controller for the personal information we obtain about you, except as described below.
